text: Virovitica-Podravina County is a county in Croatia. The county seat is Virovitica. Other notable towns are Slatina and Orahovica. ==Municipalities== Municipality Population Crnac 1,456 Čačinci 2,802 Čađavica 2,009 Gradina 3,850 Lukač 3,634 Mikleuš 1,464 Nova Bukovica 1,771 Pitomača 10,059 Sopje 2,320 Suhopolje 6,683 Špišić Bukovica 4,221 Voćin 2,382 Zdenci 1,904 ==References== Category:Counties of Croatia
